<item>
            <title>[PIG-450] PERFORMANCE:  Distinct should make use of combiner to remove duplicate values from keys.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-450</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In 2.0 distinct was improved by removing values in the map and just passing an empty tuple along with the key.  This can be further improved by adding a combiner step that passes along only the first empty tuple instead of all of them.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
